Paper: hep-th/9307070

Date: 1993-07-09

Title: Dirac Monopoles and the Angular Momentum of the Electromagnetic Field

Authors: M.C. Nemes and Saulo C.S. Silva

Comments: 4 pages IFUSP/P-1059

We present a possible solution for the long standing problem of theincompatibility of Dirac's charge quantization condition with integer valuesfor the angular momentum of the electromagnetic field.